short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Prefill common form fields with data you've entered elsewhere and save time online.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Tired of filling out the same forms over and over again? This extension makes it easy to fill common form fields with data you've already entered elsewhere. With just a few clicks, you can quickly fill in your name, address, phone number, and other details.

The extension works by capturing data as you fill out forms on various websites. This data is stored securely in your browser and can be accessed at any time. When you encounter a form that needs to be filled out, simply click the extension icon and select the data you want to use.

With this extension, you can save time and streamline your online experience. Download it now and start filling out forms with ease!
